#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/sendbymail/sendbymailplugin.cpp:64
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>This tool allows users to back-process items (as resize) before to send "
"by e-mail.</p><p>Items to process can be selected one by one or by group "
"through a selection of albums.</p><p>Different mail client application can "
"be used to process files on the network.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Esta ferramenta permite que os usuários processem itens (como "
"redimensionamento) antes de enviá-los por e-mail.</p><p>Os itens a serem "
